                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5901" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0092</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8380 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陇海之路：探寻农产品供应链扶贫金钥匙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Road of Longhai: find the golden key for industrial alleviate poverty by agricultural supply chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张晓燕，孙志忠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰州陇海绿色产业集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；产业扶贫；利益相关者；农产品供应链；2021百优案例；精准扶贫与企业社会责任专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Social Responsibility, Industrial Poverty Alleviation, Stakeholders, Agricultural Supply Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业扶贫是企业履行社会责任的重要形式，强调以贫困地区特色资源为基础，以市场需求为导向，需要稳定完善的供应链进行连接与支撑。本案例详细描述了陇海集团通过构建农产品供应链实施产业扶贫，履行企业社会责任的历程，引导学员分析打造和完善农产品供应链的关键要素，掌握利用供应链的构建来推动企业社会责任落地的方式，理解供应链上组织间的依赖关系对企业社会责任内化的影响机制，从利益相关者的角度探讨企业在社会责任履行中扮演的角色和发挥的作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Industrial poverty alleviation is an important form for corporate to fulfill their social responsibilities. It is based on the characteristic resources of poor areas, guided by market demand, and needs to be connected and supported by a stable and perfect supply chain. This case describes the process of Longhai Group in implementing industrial poverty alleviation and fulfilling Corporate Social Responsibility by construction the agricultural supply chain in detail, guides the students to analyze the key elements of building and improving the supply chain, and master the way to promote the implementation of Corporate Social Responsibility by supply chain, understand the influence mechanism of inter organizational dependence in the supply chain on the internalization of Corporate Social Responsibility, and explore the role of enterprises in the performance of social responsibility from the perspective of stakeholders.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR金字塔模型；CSR动因；CSR的利益相关者理论；CSR履行供应链运作流程；产业扶贫；供应链资源依赖和权力结构；CSR内化理论；CSR的动态环境适应性</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
